Standards-Version: 4.7.0
Homepage: https://nginx.org

Package: nginx-stable
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Provides: nginx, httpd, httpd-cgi
Conflicts: nginx, nginx-mainline
Replaces: nginx, nginx-mainline
Description: high performance web server and reverse proxy (stable)
 nginx ("engine x") is a high performance web server, reverse proxy, and
 IMAP/POP3 proxy server. It is known for its stability, rich feature set,
 simple configuration, and low resource consumption.
 .
 This package is compiled from the nginx stable release branch, which is
 updated about once a year, plus backported critical bug fixes and security
 fixes from the mainline branch. The stable branch always carries an even
 minor version number (for example, 1.30.x).

Package: nginx-stable-module-njs
Architecture: any
Depends: nginx-stable (= ${binary:Version}), ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: njs scripting dynamic modules for nginx (stable)
 This package provides the njs dynamic modules (ngx_http_js_module and
 ngx_stream_js_module) for nginx. njs is a subset of the JavaScript language
 that allows extending nginx functionality in the http and stream contexts.
 .
 The modules are compiled against the matching nginx-stable build and must be
 loaded with the load_module directive.

Package: nginx-stable-module-otel
Architecture: any
Depends: nginx-stable (= ${binary:Version}), opentelemetry-cpp, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: OpenTelemetry dynamic module for nginx (stable)
 This package provides the OpenTelemetry dynamic module (ngx_otel_module) for
 nginx. It enables distributed tracing of requests by exporting spans over
 OTLP/gRPC.
 .
 The module is compiled against the matching nginx-stable build and must be
 loaded with the load_module directive.
